description:
An aspiring V-Tuber from another world.
They'll do anything to see a smile on your face.
Although they love music and games, they're willing
to dabble in anything if it means they can have fun.

strings.default:
I know you can do 
better than that...

Not quite. 
You almost had it...

Good job. I expected 
nothing less from you.

Excellent work. 
Your performance amazes me.

Even I couldn't achieve 
such a score.
